1. Home

Hero section: Big photo of trucks/parts in action + tagline (“Quality food-truck parts & service since 1999” or similar)

Quick CTAs: “View Parts” / “Get a Quote”

Key benefits: 3-4 icons + short blurbs (“Fast shipping”, “Expert support”, “Everything you need for your truck”)

Featured product categories or bestsellers

Customer testimonials / logos

CTA again: “Request a Quote”

Footer with contact info, social links.

2. Products / Parts

Category list (e.g., “Cooking Equipment”, “Service Parts”, “Accessories”, “Custom Builds”)

Grid view of parts: photo + title + brief description + “More details”

Filtering/sorting (if many items): by category, by price, by truck type

Individual product page: high-res image gallery, spec sheet, pricing (or “call for quote”), add to cart/quote request, related parts.

3. Services

List what you do (e.g., parts sourcing, custom builds, repair/maintenance, consulting)

Each service with description + image

Case studies or featured projects (before/after of a truck build)

CTA: “Schedule a Service” or “Contact us for details”

4. About Us

Company history (since 1999)

Team photos / workshop / facilities

Why choose us / mission statement

Maybe “Our process” (how we work)

CTA: “Meet the team” / “Contact us”

5. Get a Quote / Contact

Clean contact form: Name / Email / Phone / Message / Role (owner/manager) / Truck type

Map + address/es + phone numbers + email

Maybe live chat or email link

For quotes: maybe separate “Request a Quote” page with more structured fields (truck model, part needed, budget, timeline)

FAQs: shipping info, warranty, returns, etc.

6. Resources / Blog (optional but strong)

Articles about food-truck maintenance, part upgrades, trends, trade shows

Guides (“How to choose the right fryer for your food truck”, “Maintaining your awning equipment”)

Helps build authority & SEO

CTA at end of each blog: “See our parts” or “Request a quote”

7. Footer (site-wide)

Link groups: Products, Services, About, Quote/Contact, Blog

Social icons

Legal: Terms, Privacy Policy

Newsletter signup (“Subscribe for our latest deals and inventory”)

Location(s) & contact info